reviewText: could somebody please verify this? according to Blu-ray.com this actually contains the theatrical cut of the punisher and NOT the extended cut?
Two great movies. Law Aiding Citizen is one of my all time favorites!
When I purchased this I expected the extended cut for the punisher I still love the movie I was just  hoping that it was going to be the extended cut

The pic shows the extended cut of punisher. Upon arriving in mail, it is the same artwork, but without the words "extended cut". I could care less about the steaming pile called "Law abiding citizen". Into the trash with both.  I wanted the extended cut Punisher and all I got was the theatrical version. Guess I'll stick to my DVD until they release the superior extended cut version on blu ray.
It indeed only includes the theatrical cut of Punisher.  Sadly I've been looking for bluray directors cut for a while now
Lucky I taught of purchasing but after reading the review the Punisher Extended Cut is not actually Extended Edition instead Theatrical Ver will not buying it unless confirmed if it is Uncut Ver
Love both of these movies.. And they work fine
